---
// HeroProductsBento - Asymmetric Bento Grid Product Showcase
// Modern Apple-inspired layout with varied card sizes and glassmorphism
---

<section id="productos" class="py-20 px-0 bg-gray-900 relative overflow-hidden">
	<!-- Background decorative elements -->
	<div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-5">
		<div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-[600px] h-[600px] bg-red-600 rounded-full blur-[150px]"></div>
		<div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-[500px] h-[500px] bg-amber-500 rounded-full blur-[120px]"></div>
